urdu transliteration text:
Aabad karenge hum, Hay ab karbobala nanaTere shehr-e se jaate hai, dai humko dua nana
O Grandfather (saw),
@HujjatELC

Is tarha parinde bhi, Maskan se nahi jaataGurbat me muje jaise, Hai abb jaana para nana
Even the birds don’t leave their homes,
@HujjatELC

Zainab tere rauze per beparda nahi aaiAb dekhegi sab duniya sar uska khula nana
@HujjatELC
Zainab never came to your grave without her veil,
